---
import Page from "@layouts/page";
---

<Page title="About the Show">
  <div>
    <img
      src="/img/pausefordramaticeffect.com-about-hero-2022.jpg"
      alt="PAUSE for Dramatic Effect | About the Show"
      width="700"
      height="400"
    />
  </div>
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">About the Show</h1>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">The Story</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-base-content/80">
    <strong>Douglas Dire's</strong> world is one of isolation. Once a decorated Iraq
    War veteran, he now roams the streets haunted by the memory of friends lost in
    combat. With a fleeting grip on reality, a dark past full of unresolved pain,
    and a hopeless future, Douglas stumbles upon a ring in an empty parking lot that
    forces him to confront a secret he didn't know he was keeping.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Cast</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Lamassu: <a href="https://www.stephanieycole.com/" target="_blank"
        >Stephanie Y. Cole</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>Captain Savage: <a href="#">Zach Bondo</a></li>
    <li>Amira Nazal: <a href="#">Emmett Bondo</a></li>
    <li>
      Agent Justin Time: <a href="https://createartpodcast.com/" target="_blank"
        >Timothy Kimo Brien</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>Agent Holly Day: <a href="#">Julie Bondo</a></li>
    <li>
      Douglas Dire and Zababa: <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kylebondo/"
        target="_blank">Kyle M. Bondo</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Creator</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Excutive Producer/Writer/Director: <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kylebondo/"
        target="_blank">Kyle M. Bondo</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Sound Design/Audio Editing/Foley: <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kylebondo/"
        target="_blank">Kyle M. Bondo</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Licensed Music</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://audiojungle.net/item/dramatic-orchestral-cello-ident/23210762"
        target="_blank">Dramatic Orchestral Cello Ident</a
