  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Awards</h2>
  <p class="pb-4 text-lg text-base-content/80">
    Pause for Dramatic Effect was a 2019 <a
      href="https://www.podcastawards.com/"
      target="_blank">People's Choice Podcast Awards</a
    > nominee in the <em>Fiction</em> and <em>Storyteller - Drama</em> categories.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Production Notes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Features friends and family (both volunteers and strong-armed)</li>
    <li>
      Homemade Foley sound effects using a <a
        href="https://amzn.to/3m22CRK"
        target="_blank">ZOOM H4N Pro</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Pre-recorded music from <a href="https://audiojungle.net" target="_blank"
        >Audiojungle.net</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Pre-selected, one-word writting prompt that is the title of each episode
      (that had to be included in the story)
    </li>
    <li>
      Episode scripts written the day before (and sometimes day-of) recording
      each episode
    </li>
    <li>
      In-house recording and audio editing done with <a
        href="https://www.adobe.com/products/audition.html"
        target="_blank">Adobe Audition</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Additional voices (uncredited) by Kyle M. Bondo who filled to be all of
      extra character voices (of which there were several)
    </li>
  </ul>
</Page>
